name: Delinquent penalties; seizure and sale for tax and fee
text: §249-34  Delinquent penalties; seizure and sale for tax and fee.  Any tax or fee imposed under sections 249-31 and 249-33 for any year and not paid when due shall be subject to the penalties provided in section 249-10. [L 1978, c 159, §4; am L 1981, c 50, §4]
